Ranger Help for: improve
========================

SYNTAX:      improve <str/dex/con/wis/int/chr/level>
USAGE:       Any wilderness terrain.

SUMMARY:    
Allows a Ranger to advance stats and levels. You can advance the following:
str/dex/con/wis/int/chr/level. Costs can be determined by using the 'tally'
command. Guild level increase with player level, so you cannot raise it.
However, wise Rangers will rise in guild level faster than others. 

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: stats, tally, journal, repair and glevels

